STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Timothy Edward RUNYON, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-1684 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Timothy Runyon appeals his conviction of operating while intoxicated, second offense, contending the district court erred in denying his motion to suppress evidence. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
